Name: TaskContainerExecutionInformation
SummaryComment: Contains information about the container which a task is executing.

Key.Name: State
Key.RemarksComment: This is the state of the container according to the Docker service. It is equivilant to the status field returned by "docker inspect".

Key.Name: Error
Key.SummaryComment: Detailed error information about the container.
Key.RemarksComment: This is the detailed error string from the Docker service, if available. It is equivilant to the error field returned by "docker inspect".
